: : Rodimus Prime : :
   
  Rodimus arms his arm blasters.
   
  Rodimus: Honey, many things happened in the old wars that I'm sure would confuse you. Just remember that we are Maximals. As for Waspinator, he is a little... enept. not too much of a threat but we musn't allow him to inform Hydras of our location.
   
  He turns his attention to the Maximals in the room.
   
  Rodimus Prime: Activate a jamming signal so he cant contact Hydras via a comm link. Anyone who wishes to go Pred hunting follow me.
   
  Rodimus heads from the base and towards the city perimiter in car mode.
